        "username": "LiX"
      },
      "date": "2015-06-24 12:27:14.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\nUnderstood this patch is not a perfect one. But the problem is it is not always convienent to ask users to change the config of Linux kernel, especailly when we are only building Lustre client.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 2
    },
